{"tid":2297901,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"child登仔對達哥同張敬軒既態度真係天淵之別","createTime":"2020-11-23T15:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T10:02:56.000Z","uid":272077,"like":116,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6938466a66eb1668d6458b388d18f6830d7d09","tid":2297901,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"試想下<br />\n如果達哥開post講祖國快樂<br />\n連登仔會點講？<br />\n1.達狗死全家<br />\n2.一早應該屌佢/唔應該睇佢<br />\n3.出賣backup佬<br />\n4.達狗玩outlast sleeping dogs好悶呀<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前啲人問達哥點拉低權貴<br />\n達哥答：要等時機囉 上左位一野拉佢落黎<br />\n香港娛樂圈死晒晒 CCTVB玩死樂壇<br />\n所以達哥咪上到去囉<br />\n上位受惠於網絡潮流就：達哥達叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3109240/org/f685cb2ac88cd0b586a2997e6604a9e8.jpg/v3BWRT2T5cwggBVYS9ZL3KQHclHpqztK2kOBotpDgaI?v=w1920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3109240%2Forg%2Ff685cb2ac88cd0b586a2997e6604a9e8.jpg%2Fv3BWRT2T5cwggBVYS9ZL3KQHclHpqztK2kOBotpDgaI%3Fv%3Dw1920&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4dabe9ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3109240/org/f685cb2ac88cd0b586a2997e6604a9e8.jpg/v3BWRT2T5cwggBVYS9ZL3KQHclHpqztK2kOBotpDgaI?v=w1920</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oq2692B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foq2692B.jpg&h=2fc187f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張敬軒擺明技窮 張由上季6月都無出聲 又祖國快樂又做護旗手 出面打到humhum聲仲日日幫艾辛刷鞋<br />\n拎住靚既聲線 做咩都無人屌<br />\n深紅英皇搞演唱會都冇乜連登仔屌佢 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14YViV0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14YViV0.jpg&h=3c09a562&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bb01c01cd6e7adaaea737cb0af332cbe7bc0d2b","tid":2297901,"uid":89608,"like":105,"dislike":16,"score":89,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"屌達哥黃藍問題嗰班, 只係達哥HATERS,<br />\n班人根本唔理乜野黃藍, 只係想整死達哥,<br />\n你問佢地想藍絲消失定達哥消失, 佢地應該會揀後者"},{"pid":"63b93211f